*cufflinks-1.3.0-r1 (05 Feb 2014)

  05 Feb 2014; Sergey Popov <pinkbyte@gentoo.org> -cufflinks-1.3.0.ebuild,
  +cufflinks-1.3.0-r1.ebuild, files/cufflinks-1.3.0-autotools.patch:
