  Drop hard version dep for boost, #440630, and fix compatibility with version
  1.5*; Fix gcc-4.7 problems; Fix underlinking problem

  31 Oct 2012; Diego E. Petten√≤ <flameeyes@gentoo.org> cufflinks-1.3.0.ebuild:
